data.description: Come see this nicely updated three bedroom, two bath home with a bonus room on the golf course. The home sits on one lot but is also selling the cleared lot next door.  In the home, there is beautiful wood-like laminate flooring throughout.  No carpet. The centerpiece of the living area is the gas or wood burning fireplace.  The kitchen features granite countertops, newly painted cabinets and a gas range top.  The interior has all been recently painted.  You will love the large living room, large bedrooms and especially the large bonus room which faces the golf course. There is also a wonderful 900 sf outdoor patio with a hot tub that will stay with the home. You can enjoy watching the golfers on the 13th Fairway. The roof is only two years old and a new septic system was added last year.  The two-car garage also has a back door with space for your golf cart so you can drive around the corner to the beautiful 18-hole Hilltop Lakes golf course.
